    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "A new minute species of Pristimantis (Amphibia: Anura: Craugastoridae) with a large head from the Yanachaga-Chemillén National Park in central Peru, with comments on the phylogenetic diversity of Pristimantis occurring in the Cordillera Yanachaga" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3829357>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3829349>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3829355>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3829351>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3829347>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3829361> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3829357>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Paratypes of Pristimantis boucephalus sp. nov. in dorsal (upper row) and ventral (lower row) views. From left to right: ♀ (MUSM 24479), ♂ (MUSM 24477), ♂ (MUSM 24478), juvenile (MUSM 24474). Photos by E. Lehr." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3829357/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3829349>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Live holotype (MUSM 31102, SVL 14.1 mm) of Pristimantis boucephalus sp. nov. A. Dorsal view. B. Dorsolateral view. C. Ventral view. Photos by E. Lehr." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3829349/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3829355>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Pristimantis boucephalus sp. nov., holotype (MUSM 31102). A. Dorsal view of head. B. Lateral view of head. C. Ventral view of hand. D. Ventral view of foot. Drawings by J. Moravec." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3829355/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3829351>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Preserved holotype (MUSM 31102, SVL 14.1 mm) of Pristimantis boucephalus sp. nov. A. Dorsal view. B. Ventral view. Photos by E. Lehr." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3829351/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3829347>
